<section id="faq" class="faq-section surface-section surface-elevated">
  <div class="faq-content-centered">
    <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
    <h2>Common Questions</h2>
    <p class="lead">Straight answers to the details clients ask before their signing.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="layout-container section-inner faq-inner">
    <div class="faq-container">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-question-text">
            <span class="faq-number">01</span>
            <span>What documents do I need to bring?</span>
          </span>
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="presentation"><path d="M3 6l5 5 5-5" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Bring a current government-issued photo ID for every signer. We’ll also request unsigned documents and any lender-provided instructions for review.</p>
          <p class="faq-footnote">Acceptable IDs include driver’s licenses, state IDs, passports, and military IDs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-question-text">
            <span class="faq-number">02</span>
            <span>How much does notarization cost?</span>
          </span>
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="presentation"><path d="M3 6l5 5 5-5" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>In-office notarizations start at $15 per signature. Mobile appointments add a travel fee based on distance and urgency, quoted before we dispatch.</p>
          <p class="faq-footnote">Loan packages receive flat-rate pricing that includes document scan-backs when required.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-question-text">
            <span class="faq-number">03</span>
            <span>Do you offer mobile notary services?</span>
          </span>
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="presentation"><path d="M3 6l5 5 5-5" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. We travel to homes, offices, hospitals, and secure signing locations across the Lehigh Valley and surrounding Pennsylvania regions with protective document handling.</p>
          <p class="faq-footnote">Emergency appointments outside normal hours can be arranged via phone.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-question-text">
            <span class="faq-number">04</span>
            <span>Can you notarize documents in other languages?</span>
          </span>
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="presentation"><path d="M3 6l5 5 5-5" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We notarize multilingual documents provided every signer can communicate with the notary in English to confirm willingness and understanding.</p>
          <p class="faq-footnote">For complex legal translations we can recommend vetted interpreter partners.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="faq-question-text">
            <span class="faq-number">05</span>
            <span>What is the difference between an acknowledgment and a jurat?</span>
          </span>
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="presentation"><path d="M3 6l5 5 5-5" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>An acknowledgment verifies identity and willingness; a jurat requires an oath or affirmation in our presence. We guide you to the correct certificate during scheduling.</p>
          <p class="faq-footnote">Still unsure? Share your document beforehand and we’ll confirm the correct notarial act.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
